# Address to connect to
IMAPStore gmail-remote
Host imap.gmail.com
SSLType IMAPS
AuthMechs LOGIN
User bequintao@gmail.com
PassCmd "gpg2 -q --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty -d ~/.emacs.d/mu4e/.mbsyncpass-bequintao@gmail.com.gpg"

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/Mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/Mail/gmail/INBOX
Subfolders Verbatim

Channel gmail
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Create Both
Expunge Both
Patterns * !"[Gmail]/All Mail" !"[Gmail]/Important" !"[Gmail]/Starred" !"[Gmail]/Bin"
SyncState *